<script type="text/ng-template" id="page.html">
    <section class="section section--rsvp" ng-show="page === 'rsvp'">
        <% if @invitation.present? && @invitation.persisted? %>
        <%= render :file => "invitations/edit" %>
        <% else %>
        <%= render :partial => "invitations/rsvp" %>
        <% end %>
    </section>
    <section class="section section--information" ng-show="page === 'information'">
        <p>Our wedding ceremony and reception will be held in Terrace on the Park, an iconic landmark built to be the heliport used during the 1960’s Worlds Fair in Queens, New York. Terrace on the Park is located at 52-11 111th Street, Flushing Meadows Park. <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/52-11+111th+St,+Corona,+NY+11368/@40.752004,-73.848982,14z/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x89c25fd0f5c263e9:0xec468ba86d69aad7">Click here for directions.</a></p>
        <p>The wedding ceremony will begin at 4 PM. Please try to arrive early to allow sufficient time for all guests to be seated.</p>
        <p>We have reserved a number of hotel rooms at <a href="http://coronahotelny.com/">The Corona Hotel</a> in Queens for a rate of $150 a night including tax. This hotel is a 15 minute walk or 5 minute cab ride from the wedding venue. The hotel is also just a few blocks from the “7” subway line, which takes you directly to several major tourist destinations in Manhattan, such as Grand Central Terminal, Bryant Park, and Times Square.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="section section--about" ng-show="page === 'about'">
        ABOUT PAGE
    </section>
    <section class="section section--manray" ng-show="page === 'manray'">
        MAN RAY PAGE
    </section>
</script>

